data.text:
Francis Greco and Lauren Holly were married for 12 years. They dated for 2 years after getting together in 1999 and married on 10th Mar 2001. 12 years later they divorced in 2014.

They had 3 children, George, Henry and Alexander Joseph (23).

About

Francis Greco is a Canadian Business Professional. He is famous for Husband to Lauren Holly.

Lauren Holly is a 60 year old American Actress. Born Lauren Michael Holly on 28th October, 1963 in Bristol, Pennsylvania, USA, she is famous for her roles as Deputy Sheriff Maxine Stewart in the CBS family drama series Picket Fences, NCIS Director Jenny Shepard in the CBS police procedural series NCIS, Dr. Betty Rogers in the CTV police procedural crime drama series Motive, Mary Swanson in the 1994 buddy comedy film Dumb and Dumber, Linda Lee in the 1993 biographical drama film Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story, Darian Smalls in the 1996 romantic comedy-drama film Beautiful Girls, and Gigi in the 2000 romantic fantasy comedy film What Women Want in a career that spans 1984â€“present. Her zodiac sign is Scorpio.
